Types

Lexer = object of BaseLexer
  kind: TokenKind
  token: string
  error: string
  startPos: int
  wsno: int
  multiLineStr: bool

LexerException = object of CatchableError
Parser = object
  lex*: Lexer
  prev, curr, next: TokenTuple
  lvl: Table[int, Node]
  error: string
  contents: Rope
  program: Program
  rootType: NType

TokenKind {.pure.} = enum
  TK_UNKNOWN, TK_INTEGER, TK_FLOAT, TK_STRING, TK_IDENTIFIER, TK_EOF,
  TK_LBR = "[", TK_RBR = "]", TK_COLON = ":", TK_COMMA = ",", TK_HYPHEN = "-",
  TK_ALT_STRING, TK_BACKSLASH = "\\", TK_COMMENT = "#", TK_NIL, TK_NULL,
  TK_TRUE, TK_FALSE
TokenTuple = tuple[kind: TokenKind, value: string, wsno: int, line: int,
                   col: int, pos: int]
